headline: Corrections
abstract: Corrections that appeared in print on Saturday, Jan. 25, 2020.
lead_paragraph: An article on Friday about an invitation extended to Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu to visit the White House misstated President Trump’s itinerary when he spoke to reporters aboard Air Force One. He was en route from Joint Base Andrews to Doral, Fla., to speak at the Republican National Committee’s winter meeting, not on his way back from the World Economic Forum in Davos, Switzerland.
